"enqueued. Click \"Process Pending Queue\" to run the AI pipeline."
msgstr ""
"Pemrosesan ulang lengkap. Baris antrian %1$d direset, %2$d pesan baru "
"dimasukkan ke antrian. Klik \"Proses Antrian Tertunda\" untuk menjalankan "
"pipeline AI."

